To play the game, open index.html in a modern browser.

Ludum Dare 48 hour project.

This is my game for Ludum Dare 21

The game uses the open-source Cake library: https://github.com/MichaelCereda/CakeJs

It uses an open-source A* library: https://github.com/bgrins/javascript-astar

You are the legendary hero Spartacus and your soldiers have been captured by the evil roman legions!

You must help them escape the prison and get them to exit

But the Roman Guards are trying to stop you. They'll kill your soldiers if you don't get them first!

You must move as many soldiers to the exit as possible before time runs out!

To play the game, go to ~~http://jamieclinton.com/escape/index.html~~
